        "text": "Functions used for rendering"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "511",
        "folderId": "397",
        "text": "drawball is used to draw a ball at a position, and take into account if that ball is not pocketed pocketed"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "82",
        "folderId": "397",
        "color": "#000000",
        "latex": "d_{rawball}\\left(p_{os},v\\right)=\\left\\{v=1:\\left(x-p_{os}.x\\right)^{2}+\\left(y-p_{os}.y\\right)^{2}-b_{all}^{2}\\right\\}"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "512",
        "folderId": "397",
        "text": "drawstripe is used to draw a ball at a position, and take into account if that ball is not pocketed pocketed"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "410",
        "folderId": "397",
        "color": "#388c46",
        "latex": "d_{rawstripe}\\left(p_{os},s_{v},v\\right)=\\left\\{v+s_{v}=2:\\left\\{\\left|y-p_{os}.y\\right|>s_{tripesize}s:\\left(x-p_{os}.x\\right)^{2}+\\left(y-p_{os}.y\\right)^{2}-b_{all}^{2},1\\right\\}\\right\\}"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "514",
        "folderId": "397",
        "text": "circle is a general function to draw a circle at a point with a radius"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "418",
        "folderId": "397",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "c_{ircle}\\left(p_{os},r_{adius}\\right)=\\left(x-p_{os}.x\\right)^{2}+\\left(y-p_{os}.y\\right)^{2}-r_{adius}^{2}"
      },
      {
